wminc-desc: Gyezesa wiki system eya mukuza wa wikimedia
wminc-prefinfo-language: Orurimi rwawe r'okukozesa aha Karimagyezi - ni rutaana aha wiki eriyo ne gyezesibwa
wminc-prefinfo-code: ISO 639 kodi eya orurimi Oru oriyo nokoraho ah
wminc-prefinfo-project: Toorana wikimedia purogyekiti eyi oriyo nokoraho aha
wminc-prefinfo-error: Wa torana purogyekiti eri kwenda Kodi ya orurimi.
wminc-error-move-unprefixed: Error: Orubaju oru oriyo nogyezaho ku twaara aha[[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|turwiine tugambo twokubanza ninga rwiine otugambo tugwire]].
wminc-error-wronglangcode: Enshobi: Orubaju oru rwiine [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|Kodi ya orurimi egwire]] "$1".
wminc-error-unprefixed-suggest: Enshobi: Orubaju oru tirwiine[[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|otugambo twokubanza]]! Nobasa ku ru hangaho aha [[:$1]].
wminc-error-wiki-exists: Egi wiki eriho. Nobasa ku shanga orubaju oru aha $1. Wiki yerugire ku korwa, rendaho Eshaha ninga ebiro bikye kuhitsya byoona ebyawo byazamu.
wminc-error-wiki-sister: Orubaju Oru norwa purogyekiti etaku shangwa aha. Gyenda aha $1 kubona wiki.
randombytest: Orubaju Oruta kumanywa gye orwa wiki eriyo ne gyezesibwa
wminc-viewuserlang: Reeba orurimi rwa omukozesa ogyezese wiki
action-viewuserlang: reeba orurimi rwa omukozesa na wiki eriyo ne gyezesibwa
right-viewuserlang: Reeba orurimi rwa Omukozesa na wiki eriyo ne gyezesibwa
group-test-sysop: Abebembezi bakuru ba wiki eriyo ne gyezesibwa
grouppage-test-sysop: {{ns:project}}:Abebembezi bakuru ba wiki eriyo ne gyezesibwa
wminc-listusers-testwiki: Oriyo no reeba Abakozesa abakunzire ngu wiki yabo eriyo negyezesibwa  ebe $1.
wminc-search-nocreate-nopref: Wa no sherura "$1". Torana  [[Special:Preferences| ekyorikwenda ku gyezesa aha wiki]] kwenda ngu tuku gambire ni Orubaju ki Oru was kubasa ku hangaho!
wminc-search-nocreate-suggest: Wa no sherura "$1". Nobasa ku hangaho Orubaju omu wiki yawe aha [[$3]]!
wminc-searchwiki-noresults: Tihariho ebyarugamu. Nobasa  ku sherura oriku koresa Kodi z'orurimi, amaziina ga obuhangwa nana amaziina vagari omu orurimi rwa Karimagyezi yawe ninga Orungyereza.
wminc-searchwiki-multiplematches: Oku sherura kwawe Ni ku gyenda na  endimi ezi:
wminc-searchwiki-match-nativename: "$1" ni eiziina rya $2 omu orurimi orwo.
wminc-fs-intro: Wa yakirwa aha {{SITENAME}} tambwe z'okubanza z'okukandika. Noza kuba nohaburwa waba notandikaho wiki ensya
wminc-fs-signup-text:
Waba Oine account ya Omukozesa,[$1 yeyanjuremu].waba otiine nemwe, [$2 hangaho account ya Omukozesa].
Tikiri kwetengyesa, kwonka nikihamibwa, Kandi nikitwaara obutikitiki bukye ku gi hangaho.
wminc-fs-settings-text:
Za aha[[Special:Preferences#mw-htmlform-i18n|ebirikwendwa byawe]] ohindure setingi ya wiki erikugyezesibwa.
Ekyo kubanza Ni orurimi rwa Karimagyezi yawe, Oru wa toorana omu ru tambwe rwokubanza kwonka nobasa ku ruhindura.
Ekya kabiri ni purogyekiti eyorikwenda kukoraho nana ekya kashatu ni Kodi y'orurimi rwa purogyekiti eyorikwenda kukoraho.
Waba otakumanya Kodi, hikirira [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-manual-url}}|endagiriro yenkozesa]] ninga shaba [[{{MediaWiki:Portal-url}}|Obuyambi]].
wminc-fs-userpage-text: Hati hangaho Orubaju rwawe r'okukozesa $1 rwiine na ebirikukukwataho ebikuru. Nobasa kuru reebera aha mutwe gwa Orubaju Oru.
wminc-fs-startwiki-text: Otugambo twokubanza twa wiki eriyo negyezesibwa ni $1. Nobasa ku hangaho Orubaju orukuru orwa wiki aha $2.
wminc-fs-startwiki-exists-text:
Otugambo twokubanza otwa wiki yawe ni $1. Orubaju orukuru ruri ah $2. Hati nobasas ku kwatanisa na abagambi b'orurimi kwombeka ekyanga!
Waba noyenda ku hangaho Orubaju, gyezaho ohandiikye eiziina omu bokisi y'okusherururamu aheiguru, ninga kuratirira linki eyi ora reebe.
wminc-infopage-welcome: Wa yakiirwa aha wikimedia mukuza, purogyekiti ya wikimedia Foundation ([[{{MediaWiki:Aboutpage}}|ebirikugyikwataho]])
wminc-infopage-option-startwiki:
Waba noyenda ku tandikaho egyi wiki, kuratirira
'''[$3 entambwe ezi]''' nana [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-manual-url}}|endagiriro yeitu yenkozesa]].

wminc-infopage-option-languages-existing: Nobasa ku sherura [//www.$1.org ebika by'endimi ebiriho ebya $1].
